[CENTER][B][U][SIZE=5][FONT=Arial Narrow]What is RSGD?[/FONT][/SIZE][/U][/B]
RSGD is a combination of programs made by [user]Method[/user], [user]Laz[/user], [user]Sir Tom[/user] that Deobfuscates an original jar or the current revision of RuneScape.
However the cache downloader by method in this program is outdated so please use the one located below with the other downloads.


[/CENTER]

